{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Grant 100% relief on business rates for retail, hospitality & leisure until 2024",
        "additional_details": "There are great businesses offering a range of different fitness, health, and activities venues available but many are really struggling after the pandemic.\r\n \r\nWe need the UK Government to act now to immediately remove business rates for all retail, hospitality and leisure businesses, as many are facing closure. The cost of living crisis will not just affect these businesses but also the physical and mental health of people across the whole of the UK, if you don't take action now!!\r\n \r\n#saveleisurebusinesses\r\n#actnow",
        "background": "For the 2022-23 tax year, the Government offers 50% relief on business rates for retail, hospitality and leisure businesses under certain conditions. This relief should be increased to 100% until March 2024.",
